                    <li><a href="https://telegram.me/dncuug">devdigest // net core</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://telegram.me/azure.ua">devdigest // xamarin</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://telegram.me/xamarin.ua">devdigest // azure</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2">
                <h4>Information</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/content/partners">Partners</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/content/about">About Us</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3">
                <h4>Concept</h4>
                Our community is a union of developers, who use and love Microsoft technology stack: .NET Core, Xamarin and Microsoft Azure.
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 text-right">
                <br />
                <p>Developers Digest &copy; 2017</p>
            </div>            
        </section>    
    </footer>
    
    <environment include="Development">
        <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>
        <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
        <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
